Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:06.04,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Let's hear our first request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:12.58,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,Okay, the first person is Saneyoshi Sakuya, a 9 year old third grade elementary school student from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:12.58,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:21.20,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,"Dear Detectives, good evening. I've had a pet dog for 2 years at my house. Her name is Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.08,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:18.83,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.08,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:28.02,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,She has a light brown color that reminds me of sweet kinako (roasted soybean flour), so I gave her that cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.25,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.50,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,There's a neighborhood Obaa-chan that when she goes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:36.42,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,she walks in front of our house and gives Kinako a treat. She cares so much about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:42.54,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,But there is one problem, that Obaa-chan keeps calling her Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.07,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Even though she's Kinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.07,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:52.92,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,My mother told her, "Her name isn't Tarou-chan, she's Kinako"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.61,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,but next day, she continued saying "Tarou-chan, Tarou-chan" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:02.33,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,Since I gave her that unique name, I wish that Obaa-chan would learn and use the name Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:05.46,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,I get a little sad every time she gets it wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:10.00,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,so I want help to make her remember it in a gentle manner." That's the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.94,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,That's kind of a cute request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:18.77,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Yes, it's very cute. This a request from 9 year old Sakuya. She's a very gentle girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:19.50,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:26.69,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Let's see if we succeeded in making Obaa-chan remember the dog's name with that same gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:27.64,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.62,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:28.62,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:32.84,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Ah. She's barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.23,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Here she is. Kina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.43,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's very watchful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:44.43,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.56,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.80,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,That's probably because she's hearing a new type of human voice. (Joking about his own lisp.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.55,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.31,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Ah, hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:54.94,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:55.54,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:56.41,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Sakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.14,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.45,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.76,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure you are a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.49,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Why am I feeling like you are so gentle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.80,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Thanks for the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.25,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.70,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Can we talk a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.88,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:14.42,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,The Obaa-chan in our neighborhood keeps calling Kinako, Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.23,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Since she's not a boy, I want her to call her Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.03,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,That Obaa-chan comes here everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.79,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,She comes here almost everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:24.48,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,So she gets it wrong almost daily?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.42,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I took a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.59,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,You recorded a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.55,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.77,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:33.78,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,That camera looks gentle too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:37.96,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Can I see the video of the "Tarou Obaa-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.11,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.83,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan! Tarou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:51.27,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She appears suddenly and is greeting "Tarou-chan".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.15,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.56,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.95,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.09,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Kinako is so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.09,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.18,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Oh. She's calling her Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.04,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.91,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's calling her Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.59,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,You're so lively. Liveliness is very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.26,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Kinako is so excited for that food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.26,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.26,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,What if grandma is actually a grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.24,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,What if we're the ones who are actually wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:24.04,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,That's not it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:32.36,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Oh you already eat it? You're so fast. Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.88,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's treating her like a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.82,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,There's no more. No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:46.22,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,"Ah, I want it!". You can't say that. I don't have any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.05,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Maybe she had a dog in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.35,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Oh, and the dog's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.00,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Maybe it was Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.92,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I see. That could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:03.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe she sees her old, beloved "Tarou" in Kinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.25,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.23,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's leaving like she doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.80,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Makes me want to call her Kinako-chan instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.41,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,So, she really believes the dog's name is Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:24.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm always wondering if I should correct her or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.92,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:28.44,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I understand your situation now. Correcting her feels difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.12,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,She's got a good spirit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.56,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Her aura, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:35.47,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's why I've been wondering how I could correct her without being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.05,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Oh Director, that's what I call "tender village problems".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.68,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Let's try the "Kinako challenge".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.51,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kinako challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The nonchalant "Kinako challenge"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:54.20,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,We've written Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Strategy: Casually put it in her line of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.60,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Usually there's nothing in that place right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.56,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Since it's raining, I wonder if she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.56,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yeah, will she come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:03.53,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She hasn't come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.35,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:05.88,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,She hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.52,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,So she didn't "early morning Tarou" yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:12.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,10:40 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:19.48,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Hey! Tarou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.66,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.35,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Why are you not barking? Because it rained?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.90,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:33.24,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan is teaching Kinako about rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.84,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,It rained!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.99,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,It's rained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.72,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why are you not barking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.58,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She didn't notice the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.21,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Oh wow, she's at the perfect angle right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.84,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,She's in the "Kinako angle"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.95,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.92,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Please see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:02.89,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan is watching Kinako instead of "Kinako".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.63,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,I don't have any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.35,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.16,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan? That's a fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.60,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.55,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.48,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan! Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.48,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,She didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:26.80,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Bye bye. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.28,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:39.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kinako Challenge: Failed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.73,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:43.00,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I have a suggestion, how about name her Tarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.16,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But she's a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.96,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,How many times a day she comes here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.06,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Usually twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:50.03,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,2 times?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.03,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:54.88,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,First in the morning and in the afternoon on the way back home a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.77,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,A second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The "Kinako Challenge" has 1 more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.78,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,So this is our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.53,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Sakuya, do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:09.60,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,How about put a mic in her collar and someone talk through that? To make it as if Kinako is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.40,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Make Kinako talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.72,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Huh? Put a mic in her collar and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.86,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Make her say "I'm not Tarou, I'm Kinako".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:23.44,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Since Obaa-chan likes Kinako, I think she will remember her name that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.16,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Ohhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.16,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:28.56,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Because Obaa-chan always talks to Kinako, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:35.80,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,If Tarou speaks in my voice, Obaa-chan will think "This dog is cursed."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:46.64,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Kinako looks like she's feeling our nervousness. Like "something is going to change today".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:51.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,3:50 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.42,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.83,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Oh, what's happened? Why you are in that location?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.30,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,"What's happened?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.64,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.61,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.09,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.34,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.34,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.33,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Just basking in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.96,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:30.97,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.74,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:38.47,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.76,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.18,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.72,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.15,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.29,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.04,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Tarou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.03,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I'm not Tarou, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.93,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What's happened? Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.44,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:03.44,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Can you listen to me please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.46,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,I'm a girl called Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.07,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Really? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.21,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,I'm not Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.24,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Can you call me Kinako from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.38,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.60,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Can you call me Kinako from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.66,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Chisako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.60,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.91,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Kinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.17,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.32,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Yes, Kinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:34.94,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Ok, you're Kinako. You weren't Tarou. Now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.66,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.87,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Thanks! Call me by that name ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.19,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes, I will call you Kinako from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:47.24,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan forgets things very fast you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:50.71,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,So please do your best to not forget, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.33,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.64,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,I'll write it in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.83,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan, right? Got it, got it. Kinako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.07,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Yep, it's Kinako. Kinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:08.62,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,You're called Kinako. I see. I see, I've got it. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:11.49,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,See you later ok? Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.22,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.32,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.84,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.16,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.72,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.82,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:29.29,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,I hear talking from somewhere but where is it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.36,Sakuya,Sakuya,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.55,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.15,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.31,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.97,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.16,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What, what, what? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.03,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.93,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:42.93,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:43.65,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:48.80,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,The dog is always happy to receive treats from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.14,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.13,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:54.48,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Really? I'm doing this without permission so maybe I shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:11:02.28,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,They're happy that you always say "Tarou, Tarou" and dote on him, but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:06.37,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,since her name is actually Kinako. So that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.76,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Who did I hear it was Tarou from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.61,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Yeah, who told you it was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.36,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Have you had a dog before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.07,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes, I had an Akita dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.05,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.05,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.28,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Was it Tarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.04,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,It wasn't Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.12,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,It wasn't even Tarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It wasn't Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.48,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,It wasn't Tarou I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.15,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,"You think". That's not clear either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.49,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan, you've got to learn the dog's name. Have you memorized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.11,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Yes, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.60,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.64,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,It wasn't something like Sakura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.63,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,You forget so quickly, Obaa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:54.36,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Good morning! Kinako-chan! Kinako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:01.82,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan! Good morning! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.42,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:08.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kinako challenge: Successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:08.42,Obaa-chan,Obaa-chan,0,0,0,,Kinako-chan, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.67,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.32,Erika,Erika Matsuo,0,0,0,,Adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.56,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.01,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,That Obaa-chan is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:22.32,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Obaa-chan is really a good person, as you could see, that's why Sakuya was so resistant to correct her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:27.02,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,In the end, Obaa-chan's daughter came to see her and they came back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:30.95,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,When she was asked to write the dog's name, she still wrote Chisako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:35.09,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,We were able to correct her though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:35.81,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.22,Maeda,Maeda,0,0,0,,Thanks for the assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.64,Nishida,Nishida,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
